    "/api/v1/orchestration/run": {
      "post": {
        "description": "Trigger orchestration workflow.\n\nThis endpoint executes the complete trading workflow:\n1. Fetch signals from Signal Service (T3)\n2. Map signals to orders with position sizing\n3. Submit orders to Execution Gateway (T4)\n4. Track execution and persist results\n\nArgs:\n    request: OrchestrationRequest with symbols and optional parameters\n\nReturns:\n    OrchestrationResult with complete run details\n\nRaises:\n    HTTPException 400: Invalid request\n    HTTPException 503: Dependent service unavailable\n    HTTPException 500: Internal error\n\nExamples:\n    >>> import requests\n    >>> response = requests.post(\n    ...     \"http://localhost:8003/api/v1/orchestration/run\",\n    ...     json={\n    ...         \"symbols\": [\"AAPL\", \"MSFT\", \"GOOGL\"],\n    ...         \"as_of_date\": \"2024-12-31\"\n    ...     }\n    ... )\n    >>> result = response.json()\n    >>> print(result[\"status\"])\n    'completed'\n    >>> print(result[\"num_orders_submitted\"])\n    2",
        "operationId": "run_orchestration_api_v1_orchestration_run_post",
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/OrchestrationRequest"
              }
            }
          },
          "required": true
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/OrchestrationResult"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Successful Response"
          },
          "422": {
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/HTTPValidationError"
                }
              }
            },
            "description": "Validation Error"
          }
        },
        "summary": "Run Orchestration",
        "tags": [
          "Orchestration"
        ]
      }
    },
